FILES
--------------------
Makefile
	The target "check" executes all test packages contained in this
        directory.
	Starts with the test packages for the tools, because these are used
	by the non-tool test packages.

DIRECTORIES
--------------------
common
	Files common to many test packages.
stdin-is-backupname
	Test of the tool `stdin-is-backupname'.
	This test package should be run before the non-tool packages, since
	it is used by these.
copyback
	Test of src/bin/copyback
